			<h3>British Sign Language (BSL) Users</h3>
			<p>BSL users, please click on the video opposite for further information.</p>
			<p><strong>If you are deaf or hard of hearing, you can:</strong><br>
Call RAD through their webcam portal at <a href="http://www.royaldeaf.org.uk/webcam/">http://www.royaldeaf.org.uk/webcam/</a> to speak to an adviser in BSL or text chat.</p>
			<h3>What you need to know</h3>
			<p>The information and support provided by the service is not the same as legal advice, which should only be provided by, or under the supervision of, professionally qualified lawyers.
				We recommend you consult a lawyer if you want legal advice, wish to take formal legal action or want advice on the merits of your case.</p>
